name: Alien Abduction (octogene, acroquelois, Nahalu)
description:
In a parallel dimension is a world where the rules are reversed. The humans no longer walk on the walls and the Man In Black are captured by the aliens.

Control the mind of Agent J and try to capture him through different levels !

Made for Weekly Game Jam 190. Theme "Walk on Walls"

The game is played exclusively with the mouse.

JUMP : Maintain Left Mouse click

Sound(AdhesiveWombat)

Sci-fi - Benjamin Tissot

Men in black(Alex Eline)

Clock/Timer

UFO(BoganJab)
